<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.7.6">
<l>paṭṭamkaṭ ṭippoṟṟō ṭupeytivaḷ pāṭaka mumcilampum</l>
<l>iṭṭamā kavaḷart teṭuttēṉuk keṉṉō ṭirukkaluṟāḷ</l>
<l>poṭṭappōyp puṟappaṭṭu niṉṟivaḷpū vaippūvaṇ ṇāveṉṉum</l>
<l>vaṭṭavār kuḻalmaṅkai mīrivaḷ māluṟu kiṉṟāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For me, who raised [her] providing [all her] wants,</l>
<l rend="indent">affixing [her] forehead ornament,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] adorning [her] with golden earrings,</l>
<l rend="indent">an anklet and ankle bells,</l>
<l>she has no [desire] to be with me.</l>
<l>Suddenly running, going and staying outside</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “Pūvai flower[-hued] Lord”.</l>
<l>Ladies with ringlettes in your hair! She has gone mad!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
